headline: SXY Announces Strategic Partnerships with MLP presented by DoorDash, Pickleball Central and the Carvana PPA Tour
summary: SXY, a leading U.S. beach tennis and pickleball brand, today announced a series of strategic partnerships across professional pickleball, including MLP presented by DoorDash, Pickleball Central and the Carvana PPA Tour.
